{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 147636, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 25688, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "pencil除了磁力吸附在iPadpro上和双击切换橡皮擦和一代没有区别", "timestamp": 1595062768, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 147645, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 25688, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "上学期末买的 air 3 2019 64G，加apple pencil （一代），某东 4.2k 。拿procreate 画过一两次，偶尔看论文和记笔记还行吧", "timestamp": 1595062882, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 147650, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 25688, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我的还没到，不过买的是11英寸的pro，二代笔，pro画画比较舒服，颜色比较正\n记笔记部分比较大 摸鱼要求又不高的话感觉可以air", "timestamp": 1595062913, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 147688, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 25688, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "二代pencil多的功能看起来确实鸡肋", "timestamp": 1595063275, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 147777, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 25688, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "啊呜 谢谢大家啦~", "timestamp": 1595064095, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 147808, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 25688, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "二代的磁吸收纳和充电长期使用的体验着实比一代好太多了，新iPad pro还有type C接口，真香", "timestamp": 1595064431, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 148235, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 25688, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还是pro+pencil2香啊（要是钱够的话）\npencil1的芭蕉扇充电法真的难受", "timestamp": 1595069560, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 148296, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 25688, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 啊这 (芭蕉扇充电法是什么...", "timestamp": 1595070092, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 148298, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 25688, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 呜呜呜我好容易动摇啊 看前面大家说的本来都决定买一代了 Dave一说真香我就又变二代党了", "timestamp": 1595070151, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 148434, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 25688, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "切身经验：画画水平的差别远大于一代二代的差别", "timestamp": 1595071183, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 148528, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 25688, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "同时拥有一代+二代，不画画，会记笔记，体验是长期使用二代磁吸和C口充电真的很香啊，一代笔很容易就没电了，需要插在平板屁股上充电，而且没地方放。个人感觉如果说笔的性能的话可能一二代差不多，差别更多是在使用体验上吧。而且pro的性能和屏幕也比其他平板好很多，不太差钱还是买新不买旧。供参考。", "timestamp": 1595071839, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 148664, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 25688, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "用过一代就会知道磁吸根本不是鸡肋…", "timestamp": 1595073076, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 149253, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 25688, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 就是一代笔充电的时候要插在那里 整个iPad就像一个大芭蕉扇一样……特别不方便", "timestamp": 1595080932, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 150116, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 25688, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈太真实了吧", "timestamp": 1595118516, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 150117, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 25688, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 好滴 感谢~", "timestamp": 1595118545, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 25688, "reply": 15, "tag": null, "text": "dz最近想买个iPad...主要两个用途，procreate摸鱼和记笔记\n想问问大家有什么比较合适的款式推荐嘛~\n(还有pencil的话要不要买二代诶...有点心动但是二代又只适配那几款好贵的pad（心疼地拍拍我瘪瘪的钱包...", "timestamp": 1595062617, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782595, "url": "", "vote": {}}}